txt.en: 'You little wretches better find something before I tear it out of your hides!'
'Oi there, let's keep an eye on these pale-folk slackjaws!'
'Now you will fall to my blade!'
'Stop your slacking and put your whip to work on these pale-folk!'
'You slaughtered my troops.... Time to pay you three-fold!'
'They find anything over there?'
'Found nothing yet. Piztor and Unudhu are going to get slaughtered.'
'This is a waste of time. When do we get to taste the flesh of Men?'
'Nothing yet.... Maybe we'll be in charge soon.'
Chieftain G没rsh bellows, 'You maggots were supposed to report in an hour ago!'
'Hold your tongue or I'll rip it out of your head!'
'Piztor! Unudhu! You sluggards had best get to the garden... quickly!'
'It's about time you bring me my pale-folk!'
'Back for more? The result will be the same!'
'These ruins are ours now! Still, I thank you for relieving the boredom. Get them!'
'Well... well... intruders. A bit o' sport instead of drudgery! Die!'
'Get a move on you soft-headed fools. We got to get a message to G没rsh.'
'G没rsh didn't put you in charge.'
An inhuman bellow rips through the Library echoing off the walls.
'Get them!'
'The little maggots are all working!'
'Work harder you little maggots or I'll shine my armour with your blood.'
'I'm not afraid to shred your hide as well as theirs.'
'C'mon you little maggots.'
'Keep up with me wretches!'
'Mind your heads you little terrors.'
'Keep up, wretches or feel my boots!'
'Find anything yet?'
'We gotta find something in this mess.'
'Nothing here but useless books!'
'Piztor and Unudhu are worried that G没rsh is gonna gut them.'
